msgid "(mock search grid, 3 columns)"
msgstr "(grille de recherche simulee, 3 colonnes)"

msgid "- First available profile -"
msgstr "- Premier profil disponible -"

msgid "- Select -"
msgstr "- Selectionner -"

msgid "1-based index. Card is inserted after this result row."
msgstr "Index base 1. La carte est inseree apres cette ligne de resultat."

msgid "<strong>1. Create a promo card</strong> — pick an SDC pattern (search push, icon, CTA), edit content and appearance with live preview."
msgstr "<strong>1. Creer une carte promo</strong> — choisissez un motif SDC (push recherche, icone, CTA), editez le contenu et l'apparence avec apercu en direct."

msgid "<strong>2. Add a placement</strong> — bind the card to a View display, set row position or interval, rotation, and optional conditions."
msgstr "<strong>2. Ajouter un emplacement</strong> — liez la carte a un affichage Views, definissez position ou intervalle, rotation et conditions optionnelles."

msgid "<strong>3. Verify on front</strong> — open the target search page and confirm the card appears between offer results."
msgstr "<strong>3. Verifier en front</strong> — ouvrez la page de recherche cible et confirmez que la carte apparait entre les resultats."

msgid "@count card(s) are not attached to any placement."
msgstr "@count carte(s) ne sont rattachees a aucun emplacement."

msgid "@enabled active"
msgstr "@enabled actif(s)"

msgid "@enabled enabled"
msgstr "@enabled active(s)"

